				acxPsu2TypeNA(15),
				acxPsu2TypeLuminatoPSU(16)
				}
			ACCESS read-only
			STATUS mandatory
			DESCRIPTION
				"Detected power supply 2 type.
				2: ICON6300 PSU: Status OK
				4: ICON6300 PSU: One or more voltages failed.
				8: No PSU at this slot present.
				15: Device doesn't support automatic power supply type detection.
